       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. OVDROUT2.
      * IDENTITY-REMEDIATION ROUTER USING THE OFFICIAL OVD REGISTRY.
       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
       DATA DIVISION.
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
       COPY OVDREG2.
       01  WS-ROUTE          PIC X(6) VALUE 'MANUAL'.
       01  WS-VERIFIED-COUNT PIC 9(4) VALUE ZERO.
       PROCEDURE DIVISION.
       1000-MAIN.
           ACCEPT WS-OVD-CODE
           PERFORM 2000-ROUTE-DOCUMENT
           DISPLAY 'ROUTE: ' WS-ROUTE
           DISPLAY 'VERIFIED: ' WS-VERIFIED-COUNT
           STOP RUN.
       2000-ROUTE-DOCUMENT.
           IF VALID-OVD2
              ADD 1 TO WS-VERIFIED-COUNT
              MOVE 'NORMAL' TO WS-ROUTE
           ELSE
              MOVE 'MANUAL' TO WS-ROUTE
           END-IF.
